caller_intent: The caller needed assistance canceling insurance on a totaled car and adding a new car to their policy.
resolution_steps: Agent confirmed Jamie was unavailable and asked if the caller was open to speaking with another agent.
Caller agreed to speak with another agent.
Agent offered to connect the caller with an agent who could handle the cancel-and-add request.
knowledge_required: Insurance policy cancellation and addition processes
Handling customer requests for policy changes
summary: A caller requested help canceling insurance on a totaled vehicle and adding a new car. Jamie was unavailable, so the agent offered to connect the caller with another agent to handle the request. The call ended with the agent promising to assist.
